    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a speed-sensitive variable M-differential for optimal lateral traction. Crucially, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings were serviced to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. With a well-sorted suspension geometry and firm damping, this chassis remains exceptionally communicative and track-ready.",
