    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior features a deep metallic finish that retains a brilliant shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment where the premium leather upholstery remains supple and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control and heated seats, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it has been serviced at regular intervals with a full logbook available for review. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm yet comfortable. Recently fitted with a fresh set of all-season tires and having passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection last month, this car is ready for its next owner to drive away with total peace of mind.",
